title: 2012 - The Little Green God of Agony.cbr
description:
Little Green God of Agony
24 Pages

Web comic by Stephen King available on his website. Took the raw images, made a cover from his art for the story, and made a proper comic book in CBR format.

Intro

Release Date: October, 15 2012

Little Green God of Agony is a serial eComic produced by StephenKing.com with Dennis Calero.

Katherine "Kat" MacDonald is an RN hired to care for wealthy client, Andrew Newsome, who has gone from doctor to doctor tyring to find a quick cure for his lingering pain to no avail. She is convinced that he would overcome the injuries he sustained in an airplane crash but he is unwilling to endure the pain of physical therapy. In desperation, Newsome has hired a healer, Reverend Rideout, who promises to "expel" his pain.
